    <item>
      <title>Abrdn 快速崛起的临时首席执行官面临根深蒂固的挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/abrdn-s-fast-rising-caretaker-ceo-faces-deep-rooted-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加入 Abrdn Plc 七个月后，贾森·温莎 (Jason Windsor) 发现自己迅速晋升到英国资产管理行业最艰难的职位之一：掌管这家陷入困境的 5,070 亿英镑（合 6,450 亿美元）公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/abrdn-s-fast-rising-caretaker-ceo-faces-deep-rooted-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 14:38:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲁本兄弟押注 20 亿美元波多黎各开发项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/billionaire-reuben-brothers-bet-on-2-billion-puerto-rico-resort</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鲁本兄弟 (Reuben Brothers) 和三规则资本 (Three Rules Capital) 提交了一份在波多黎各进行价值超过 20 亿美元的开发项目的总体规划，该项目拥有自己的私人机场并享有加勒比海的景观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/billionaire-reuben-brothers-bet-on-2-billion-puerto-rico-resort</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 22:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着房地产行业的痛苦挥之不去，喜达屋 100 亿美元的房地产投资信托基金转向生存模式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/starwood-reit-sets-drastic-redemption-limits-on-liquidity-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁巴里·斯特恩利希特 (Barry Sternlicht) 坚信，房地产市场只需再多一点时间就会反弹。他的 100 亿美元喜达屋房地产收入信托基金的许多投资者不太确定——现在就想拿回他们的钱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/starwood-reit-sets-drastic-redemption-limits-on-liquidity-crunch</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 19:05:22 GMT</pubDate>
